Dresden - August 26-27, 1813 &ndash; &ldquo;God has uttered His judgement. He was of your opnion.&rdquo;

The Thames - October 5, 1813 &ndash; &ldquo;Remember the Raisin!&rdquo;

La Rothi&egrave;re - February 1, 1814 &ndash; &ldquo;What will they say in Paris after this victory?&rdquo;

Lundy&rsquo;s Lane - July 25, 1814 &ndash; Butchery at Dusk

